title: A Nice Chat With Alana Haim!
description:
Alana Haim.. You know her from her widely successful band of sisters, HAIM. You're about to recognize her from her breakthrough role on Licorice Pizza.. and some of us may know her from her super enviable relationships! We talk to someone straight from the Swiftie squad, and we have a lot of questions for her! From work, to family, to scary movie moments that weren't meant for the big screen, to future plans..... Alana reveals all!
What should we have asked her? What would you like to? And what would you like from us? Please let us know! We love hearing from you and there are a lot of ways to reach us!
